        </div>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">Specifications</h3>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C] w-1/2">Model Type</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">Alfa Laval MAB 206S-24-60</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C]">Rated Capacity</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">36 GPM on Diesel Fuel<br/>28 GPM on Turbine Lube Oil<br/>19 GPM on Hydraulic Oil</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C]">Sludge Space</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">0.88 Gallons</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C]">Motor HP</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">7.5 HP</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C]">Voltages</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">230 / 460 V</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MAB 207 -->
      <div id="mab-207" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-4">Alfa Laval MAB 207 Centrifuge</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start mb-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
              The MAB 207 is a high-capacity model rated at 48 GPM on diesel fuel, with a 10 HP motor and 1.10 gallon sludge space. In addition to diesel, lube oil, and hydraulic oil purification, the MAB 207 is also rated for biodiesel glycerin separation at 32 GPM, making it a popular choice for biodiesel production facilities.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img
              src="/images/alfa-laval-mab-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-MAB207-Biodiesel-300x300.jpg"
              alt="Alfa Laval MAB-207 50 GPM Biodiesel Separation Centrifuge"
              width="300" height="300"
              loading="lazy"
              class="rounded-lg mx-auto"
            />
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">50 GPM Biodiesel Separation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">Specifications</h3>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C] w-1/2">Model Type</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">Alfa Laval MAB 207S-24-60</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C]">Rated Capacity</td>
                <td class="py-3 font-mono">48 GPM on Diesel Fuel<br/>40 GPM on Turbine Lube Oil<br/>32 GPM on Biodiesel Glycerin Separation<br/>25 GPM on Hydraulic Oil</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
