        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start mb-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
              The MAB 209 is the largest model in the Alfa Laval MAB series, rated at 78 GPM on diesel fuel with a 15 HP motor and the largest sludge space in the series at 2.00 gallons. Like the MAB 207, the MAB 209 is also rated for biodiesel glycerin separation at 52 GPM, making it suitable for high-throughput biodiesel production operations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img
              src="/images/alfa-laval-mab-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-MAB209-Biodiesel-Centrifuge.jpg"
              alt="Alfa Laval MAB 209 Biodiesel Glycerol Centrifuge"
              width="450" height="450"
              loading="lazy"
              class="rounded-lg mx-auto"
            />
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Alfa Laval MAB 209 Biodiesel Glycerol Centrifuge</p>
